    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The book of Nathan ... - On the \"books\" here mentioned, see the introduction to Chronicles, the second note.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "We hear nothing of Iddo in Kings: but he is mentioned below twice 2 Chronicles 12:15; 2 Chronicles 13:22. In the latter of these passages he is called not \"the seer,\" but \"the prophet.\" He seems to have been the author of three works:",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "We hear nothing of Iddo in Kings: but he is mentioned below twice ",
